["Salome Receives the Head of John the Baptist is an oil on canvas painting by Matthias Stom, probably painted around 1630\u20131632 in Rome. It is now in the National Gallery, London, to which it was presented by the Trustees of Sir Denis Mahon's Charitable Trust via the Art Fund in 2013.[1]","This painting-related article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]